---
title: Beef and Black Bean Chili with Cheddar Cheese and Sour Cream
description: Nothing says cold weather food like a big bowl of warm chili! In this oh -so-quick and tasty version, beef is stewed with black beans. It wouldn't be chili without the fixins', so we're topping it off with sour cream, cheddar cheese and spiced tortilla chips!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chili-au-boeuf-et-aux-haricots-noirs-e862033a.jpg
